author: Valdemārs Brožs
quote: "In harmony with earth and sky,"
subject: The Nature Poets of the Baltic States (Early 20th century)
permalink: /The Nature Poets of the Baltic States (Early 20th century)/Valdemārs Brožs/Valdemārs Brožs - Eternal Harmony
---

In harmony with earth and sky,
Life dances on, as years go by,
In the rustling leaves, a symphony,
Nature sings of eternity.

With every heartbeat, a promise made,
To cherish the paths that we have laid,
In the beauty of nature, we find our grace,
In this sacred, timeless space.

- Valdemārs Brožs
